Download tomcat 7.0.106 tar.gz from offical website https://archive.apache.org/dist/tomcat/tomcat-7/v7.0.106/bin/ in /opt directory

After downloading, navigate to /opt/apache-tomcat-7.0.106/bin and execute the following commands to start/stop the tomcat:
sh startup.sh
sh shutdown.sh

Once tomcat is running, access the tomcat from browser with IP:8080
